== 與人類的關係 ==
=== 食物 ===
一些蝌蚪會被人類當做食物。[[紅點齒蟾|紅點齒蟾]]的蝌蚪因為特大，體長達{{convert|10|cm}}<ref name=Li>{{Cite journal| last = Li| first = Cheng| coauthors = Xian-Guang Guo, Yue-Zhao Wang| year = 2011| title = Tadpole types of Chinese megophryid frogs (Anura: Megophryidae) and implications for larval evolution| journal = Current Zoology| volume = 57| issue = 1| pages = 93-100}}</ref>，而被中國人當做食物<ref>{{IUCN2013.1| id = 57600| title = Oreolalax rhodostigmatus| assessors = Fei Liang, Wu Guanfu| year = 2004| downloaded = 22 October 2013}}</ref>，但實際被食用的蝌蚪並不局限於此。在印度，''[[Clinotarsus_curtipes|Clinotarsus curtipes]]''的蝌蚪也是一種食物<ref>{{IUCN2013.2| id = 58583| title = Clinotarsus curtipes| assessors = Biju, S.D.; Dutta, Sushil and Inger, Robert| year = 2004| downloaded = 4 May 2014}}</ref>。[[秘魯|秘魯]]人將''[[Telmatobius_mayoloi|Telmatobius mayoloi]]''的蝌蚪當做藥物和食物<ref>{{IUCN2013.1| id = 57350| title = Telmatobius mayoloi| assessors = Javier Icochea, Edgar Lehr| year = 2004| downloaded = 23 October 2013}}</ref>。

=== 神話及民俗 ===
[[林純聲|林純聲]]和[[大林太良|大林太良]]分別在1930和1960年代於緬甸[[佤族|佤族]]地區，搜集到有關蝌蚪變成人類的神話傳說<ref>{{Cite journal| last = 李| first = 子賢| year = 2010| title = 神话王国诸相——对云南少数民族神话总体特征及存续的解读| journal = 云南师范大学学报：哲学社会科学版| issue = 6| pages = 67-76}}</ref>。據[[詹姆斯·喬治·斯科特|詹姆斯·喬治·斯科特]]所述，這是佤族名為Ya Htawm和Ya Htai的兩位女性祖先，她們在少年時是大湖Nawng Hkaeo中的蝌蚪（rairoh）<ref>Scott, James George, Sir. 1935. ''The Wa or Lawa: Head-Hunters. In Burma and Beyond.'' p. 292</ref>。

民國的妓女曾藉助吃蝌蚪來打胎<ref>{{cite web| url=http://news.ifeng.com/history/video/detail_2013_09/09/29450749_0.shtml?_from_ralated| title=民国妓女生存实录：月事时也接客 吃蝌蚪打胎| publisher=鳳凰網| accessdate=2014-06-04| archive-date=2019-09-24| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924175816/http://news.ifeng.com/history/video/detail_2013_09/09/29450749_0.shtml?_from_ralated| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

